# Secrets — never commit
.env
**/.env

# Runtime state / bind-mount data (back up separately, don't version)
**/data/
**/db/
**/images/
**/redis/
**/conf/
**/work/
**/cache/
**/lib/
# Runtime config dirs — ignore live data, but ship starter/example files.
**/config/*
!**/config/*.example
!**/config/services.yaml
!**/config/widgets.yaml
!**/config/settings.yaml
!**/config/bookmarks.yaml
!**/config/docker.yaml
**/beszel_data/
**/beszel_agent_data/
**/beszel_socket/
**/.admin-password
**/media/
**/downloads/
uptime-kuma/scripts/

# Wiki — built artifact (source lives in home-config foss-setup/wiki/)
wiki/site/
**/pgdata/
# unbound DNSSEC trust anchor auto-updates (runtime state, not config)
unbound/unbound/root.key
unbound/unbound/var/root.key

# Secrets/runtime files caught by the 2026-07-09 docs-debt audit — never track
ntfy/.healthchecks-token
ntfy/.phone-password
**/.env.bak*
**/*.pid

